			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Would like to tell you about these sharks.  If you are trying to get the rod near the sunken ship for the staff of the wheel quest, these guys like to inhabit that area.  I was a level 30 wizard when i tried to dive in and get the rod.  This thing seemed to attack for 101, 65, 20 hit, in that order, with a couple misses here and there.  Luckily i was close to shore, made it with 20 hp left, but be warned, they like the sunken ship area
				</font>
